thread.title: Ice Dancing Has a Problem: Not Enough Men

author: Betsy McKay
title: Ice Dancing Has a Problem: Not Enough Men
text:
Helena Fisher, an ice dancer, is working up a new program. It features twizzles, Latin rhythms, and, she hopes, a peacock blue dress.
One element it doesn’t have: a man. “It’s extremely hard to find a partner,” says the 19-year-old from Marietta, Ga., who trains for competitions.
